# Ripgrep ignore patterns for Babel public repo
# Prevents Glob/Ripgrep timeouts on unscoped searches (20s default timeout)
# Per CLAUDE.md Environment Gotcha #3

# Build artifacts and dependencies
node_modules/
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Generated runtime paths (never search these)
runs/
artifacts/
runtime/

# Git internals
.git/

# CI artifacts
coverage/
